Bestiary: {
	BucketZombie: This zombie took a larger hit to its intelligence than most others of its ilk, causing it to inexplicably think that buckets were, in fact, a great defensive option.
	GiantZorm: A massive cousin of the zorm, these creatures, transformed further by the effects of ancient magicks, tunnel through the ground in search of living beings to consume.
	ZombieBat: Zombified bats that flutter through the caves underneath the surface.
	ZombieEye: A servant of Chthulu that fell to the undead horde.
	ZombieSlime: A slime ravaged by the undead horde. Blood permeates its gelatinous body.
	ZombifiedMummy: A mummy brought back to the land of the living as an undead abomination.
	Zombunny: A poor bunny cursed by undeath. It prowls the day and night in search of victims.
	Zorm: A giant worm transformed by the undeath energy that permeates the land.
}

